# UI System — PayPal Fraud Intelligence Dashboard

> Self-contained design system + component reference for a fintech anti-fraud proof-of-concept.
> Drop this into your project's `CLAUDE.md` or similar AI-instructions file.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Tool |
|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 14+ (App Router, TypeScript) |
| CSS | Tailwind CSS v4 (utility-first, CSS-first config) |
| Icons | lucide-react (stroke-based SVGs) |
| Animations | framer-motion (page transitions) + CSS keyframes |
| Charts | recharts |
| Toasts | sonner |
| Forms | react-hook-form + zod |
| Font | Space Grotesk (Google Fonts via `next/font`) |

### Tailwind v4 Setup

```bash
npm i tailwindcss @tailwindcss/postcss
```

`postcss.config.mjs`:
```js
export default { plugins: { "@tailwindcss/postcss": {} } };
```

`globals.css` top line:
```css
@import "tailwindcss";
```

No `tailwind.config.ts` needed — v4 uses CSS-first configuration.

