## Design Philosophy

- **Monochrome palette** — neutrals only. No rainbow. Professional, serious, cybersecurity feel.
- **Warm grays** — stone/warm-gray tones, not cold blue-grays.
- **Semantic color only where critical** — red for active fraud alerts, green for cleared, amber for review-needed.
- **Dark mode first-class** — `[data-theme="dark"]` CSS attribute on `<html>`.

