## Icon Rules

```tsx
// Standard — lucide-react, always strokeWidth={1.5}
import { Shield, AlertTriangle, CheckCircle } from "lucide-react";

// Stat card icon
<div className="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-tertiary)] flex items-center justify-center">
  <Shield className="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--text-secondary)] shrink-0" strokeWidth={1.5} />
</div>

// Nav icon
<AlertTriangle className="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--text-tertiary)] shrink-0" strokeWidth={1.5} />

// Active nav
<CheckCircle className="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--brand-primary)] shrink-0" strokeWidth={1.5} />
```

**RULES:**
- NEVER `hover:opacity-*` on buttons with icons (causes GPU wiggle). Use `hover:bg-*` instead.
- NEVER `transition-all` on buttons. Use `transition-colors` or `transition-opacity`.
- ALWAYS `shrink-0` on SVG icons inside flex containers.

