## Animations (CSS Keyframes)

```css
/* Shimmer loading skeleton */
@keyframes shimmer {
  0% { background-position: 200% 0; }
  100% { background-position: -200% 0; }
}
.animate-shimmer { animation: shimmer 2.5s ease-in-out infinite; }

/* Card reveal */
@keyframes card-in {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
.animate-card-in { animation: card-in 0.35s ease-out both; }

/* Dropdown menu */
@keyframes dropdown-in {
  0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95) translateY(-4px); }
  100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); }
}
.animate-dropdown-in {
  animation: dropdown-in 0.15s ease-out both;
  transform-origin: top right;
}

/* Pulse for live alerts */
@keyframes alert-pulse {
  0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.4); }
  50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0); }
}
.animate-alert-pulse { animation: alert-pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite; }
