## Design Principles Checklist

- [ ] Monochrome palette — no colored gradients, neutrals only
- [ ] Semantic color restricted to fraud severity (red/amber/green/indigo)
- [ ] All interactive elements have hover + focus states
- [ ] `transition-colors` on buttons (never `transition-all`)
- [ ] `shrink-0` on all SVG icons in flex
- [ ] Cards: `rounded-2xl`, subtle shadow, `border border-[var(--border-primary)]`
- [ ] Modals: 3-section (header `border-b`, body, footer `border-t py-4`)
- [ ] Typography: max 4 sizes per page (title, heading, body, caption)
- [ ] Spacing: multiples of 4px only
- [ ] Dark mode: test every component in both themes
- [ ] Animations: 150-300ms, `ease-out` for entrances
- [ ] Loading: skeleton shimmer, never raw spinners for page content
- [ ] Empty states: icon + title + description, always

